Citation

Kermany, Daniel; Zhang, Kang; Goldbaum, Michael (2018). Labeled Optical Coherence Tomography (OCT) and Chest X-Ray Images for Classification. Mendeley Data, v2. DOI: 10.17632/rscbjbr9sj.2
